# 🤖 AI ChatBot using Java

## 📌 Overview

This project is a simple AI-based ChatBot developed using Java. It provides real-time responses to user queries through a graphical user interface (GUI). The chatbot uses basic Natural Language Processing (NLP) techniques and a rule-based response engine to understand user input and generate appropriate responses.

The project demonstrates Object-Oriented Programming (OOP), Java Swing, and basic Artificial Intelligence concepts.

---

## ✨ Features

- Interactive Java Swing GUI
- Rule-Based Chatbot
- Basic NLP Processing
- Keyword Matching
- Knowledge Base (FAQ)
- Modular Object-Oriented Design
- Easy to Extend
- Fast Response Generation

