## 📂 Project Structure

```
AIChatBot
│
├── Main.java
├── chatbotgui.java
├── Engine.java
├── database.java
└── nlpprocessing.java
```

---

## 📄 Module Description

### Main.java
- Starts the application.
- Launches the chatbot GUI.

### chatbotgui.java
- Builds the graphical user interface.
- Handles user interaction.
- Displays chat messages.

### Engine.java
- Core chatbot logic.
- Generates responses based on user queries.
- Connects NLP module with the knowledge base.

### database.java
- Stores chatbot knowledge.
- Uses HashMap to manage FAQs and predefined responses.

### nlpprocessing.java
- Performs basic Natural Language Processing.
- Converts text to lowercase.
- Removes special characters.
- Tokenizes user input.

---

## 🧠 AI Techniques Used

The chatbot uses a simple rule-based AI approach.

### NLP Techniques

